Package: http-reverse-proxy
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: HTTP reverse proxy differenciating by Host: header
 Finds its backends according to Host header from a configuration file,
 and keeps connections to all of them for as long as possible. Reestablishes
 connections in the background and balances over them using a round-robin
 algorithm.
